.title Help: Auditing Utilities Package
ABOUT THIS PACKAGE
The Auditing package provides auditing facilities for
recording and reporting all security-related events that
occur on the system.

After installing this package you may want to create a
separate /var/audit file system.  See the Installation
Handbook for details.

EXITING THE PACKAGE SELECTION MENU
Press <Enter> to enter your selections and to return to the
Install Menu.

EXITING HELP
Press <Esc> to return to the Package Selection menu.
Press <F1> for more help.
